		<main class="mx-auto mt-4">
			<h1 class="mb-2 border-b-2 text-base border-slate-300">HOME</h1>
			<p>
        A software engineer with extensive experience in web development, including
        traditional MVC, serverless, SQL, and more. Creative problem solver regardless of the language,
        with a focus on Ruby, PHP, and Javascript. Creator of programming education,
        music tech, and open source content, which you can find on my YouTube, Twitter, GitHub, etc...
			</p>
      <section class="mt-4">
        <h2 class="mb-2 border-b-2 text-base border-slate-300">QUICK LINKS</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a class="text-lg underline" href="https://www.github.com/stevetwitte">github.com/stevetwitte</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="text-lg underline" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/stevetwitte">linkedin.com/in/stevetwitte</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="text-lg underline" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1E8jNiwzaaZ34FYF0X69w2GU36FFupCsS/view?usp=sharing">resume-stephen-witte.pdf</a>
